of these shares was $5,059 for the same periods. treasury shares as of december
31, 2002, 2001 and 2000 were 171,834,950; 174,289,720 and 136,385,222. there
were no treasury shares acquired for the year ended december 31, 2002. treasury
shares acquired for the years ended december 31, 2001 and 2000, were 40,734,500
and 41,782,234. treasury shares issued for share-based plans for the years ended
december 31, 2002, 2001 and 2000, were 2,454,770; 2,830,002 and 7,753,909.
