the effective income tax
rate for 2002 was 27.1% compared with 20.7% in 2001 and 29.0% in 2000. the 2002
effective income tax rate of 27.1% varies from the federal statutory tax rate of
35%, principally due to foreign sales corporation (fsc) and extraterritorial
